VHola todos, hago este blog para publicar algunas cosas que se me van ocurriendo. Relatos, cuentos cortos, etc. También puedo poner letras de canciones que me gustan y bueno, veremos que más. Gracias por la visita.<br /><br /><br /><br /><b><u>Kindom of Doom (By The Good, the Bad &amp; the Queen)</u></b><br /><br /><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 11px;">Friday night</span><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 11px;"><br /></span><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 11px;">In the Kingdom of Doom</span><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 11px;"><br /></span><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 11px;">Oh, ravens fly</span><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 11px;"><br /></span><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 11px;">Across the moon</span><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 11px;"><br /></span><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 11px;"><br /></span><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 11px;">All in now</span><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 11px;"><br /></span><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 11px;">There\u2019s a noise in the sky</span><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 11px;"><br /></span><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 11px;">Following all the rules</span><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 11px;"><br /></span><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 11px;">And not asking why</span><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 11px;"><br /></span><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 11px;"><br /></span><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 11px;">[Chorus]</span><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 11px;"><br /></span><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 11px;">When the sunset wheel begins</span><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 11px;"><br /></span><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 11px;">Turning into the night</span><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 11px;"><br /></span><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 11px;">I see everything in black and white</span><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 11px;"><br /></span><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 11px;">And then...</span><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 11px;"><br /></span><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 11px;"><br /></span><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 11px;">Drink all day</span><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 11px;"><br /></span><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 11px;">Coz the country's at war</span